$ON_ZBPTNUM
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ZBPTNUM From W1FCY2
Return

$AV_ZBPTNUM
If clalev([F:BPT])=0 : Local File BPCARRIER [BPT] : Endif
Call LECTURE("BPT",num$([M]BPTNUM(indice)),"") From CONTOBJ
zc = [F:BPT]BPTSHO
Gosub _AFF
Return

