$ON_SPAOPEIGIC
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_SPAOPEIGIC From W1FCY2
Onevent INIT_AREA Call D_SPAOPEIGIC(zc) From W1FCY2
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_SPAOPEIGIC(zc) From W1FCY2
Return

$AV_SPAOPEIGIC
## Action STD
Call AV_SPAOPEIGIC(zc) From SUBFCYB
If [M]FMTESP<>""
 Chgfmt [M]SPAOPEIGIC(indice) With [M]FMTESP
Else
 Chgfmt [M]SPAOPEIGIC(indice) With "-K:1X"
Endif
Gosub _AFF
Return

Subprog D_SPAOPEIGIC(VALEUR)
